graph LR
    Notebooks[Workbench Images<br/>Notebooks]

    %% External Dependencies - Base OS and Runtimes
    Notebooks -->|base OS| UBI9[UBI9/RHEL9 Base<br/>9.x]
    Notebooks -->|runtime| Python[Python<br/>3.9, 3.11]

    %% External Dependencies - Jupyter
    Notebooks -->|UI framework| JupyterLab[JupyterLab<br/>3.5-4.2]
    Notebooks -.->|extensions| Elyra[Elyra<br/>AI/ML Pipeline IDE]

    %% External Dependencies - ML Frameworks
    Notebooks -.->|deep learning| PyTorch[PyTorch<br/>2.x]
    Notebooks -.->|ML framework| TensorFlow[TensorFlow<br/>2.x]
    Notebooks -.->|data science| Pandas[Pandas<br/>1.5-2.x]
    Notebooks -.->|numerical| NumPy[NumPy<br/>1.24+]
    Notebooks -.->|ML library| ScikitLearn[Scikit-learn<br/>1.2+]

    %% External Dependencies - GPU Support
    Notebooks -.->|NVIDIA GPU| CUDA[CUDA Toolkit<br/>11.8, 12.x]
    Notebooks -.->|AMD GPU| ROCm[ROCm<br/>5.x, 6.x]
    Notebooks -.->|Intel GPU| IntelExt[Intel Extension<br/>for PyTorch]

    %% External Dependencies - IDE Variants
    Notebooks -.->|R IDE| RStudio[RStudio Server<br/>2024.04.2]
    Notebooks -.->|VS Code| CodeServer[Code Server<br/>Latest]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    Notebooks -->|spawned by| NotebookController[odh-notebook-controller]
    Notebooks -->|displayed in| Dashboard[odh-dashboard]
    Notebooks -.->|alternative spawner| KubeflowController[kubeflow-notebook-controller]

    %% External Services
    Notebooks -->|image pulls| Quay[Quay.io Registry]
    Notebooks -->|image pulls| InternalRegistry[OpenShift Internal<br/>Registry]
    Notebooks -->|package install| PyPIMirror[PyPI/Conda Mirrors]
    Notebooks -->|data access| S3[S3 Storage]
    Notebooks -->|source code| GitRepos[Git Repositories]

